name: mikrotik
os: RouterOS
os_family: RouterOS
version: 0.0.2
release: 1
minimum_version: 3006
summary: Agentless, schema-driven config management for MikroTik RouterOS
description: >
  Declarative RouterOS configuration management driven from a Salt master via
  salt-sproxy (no agent, no proxy daemon on the device). Ships a librouteros
  proxy module, a schema-driven reconciliation engine (execution module) and
  state module supporting singleton, keyed-collection and ordered
  (comment-tag-keyed) RouterOS paths, plus a commit-confirm router-side
  auto-revert for lockout-risky changes. Reconciliation design derived from the
  community.routeros Ansible collection (GPL-3.0-or-later).
top_level_dir: mikrotik
